OPT USA - Offshore Pipeline Technology
22 & 23 October 2001, J W Marriott, Houston, Texas

www.ibcenergy.com/ep1118/?source=ep1118elc

Plus a one day intensive seminar
Latest developments in Design, Analysis and Installation of
Deep and Ultra Deepwater Risers
24 October 2001, J W Marriott, Houston

Organizing Committee:

*Frans Kopp, Shell International Exploration & Production
Deepwater Services
