Topics Highlights:

* The Banjo and Seahawk Oil and Gas Export Pipelines 16 and
18 Inch Pipelines Installed by the CSO Deep Blue, Fraser
Moore, Project Manager - Banjo/Seahawk Pipeline Project,
Coflexip Stena Offshore
* Nile Subsea Development Reeled Flowline and SCR - A
Project Overview, Gary Imm, BP and Majid Al-Sharif and
Richard Griffiths, J P Kenny, Inc
* Blue Stream Project - a driver for Pipelaying Technology
Development, Stefano Bianchi and Mauro Brambilla, Saipem
S.p.A.
* New Pipeline Technology Achievements Spur Development of
Cost Effective Gas Gathering Systems, Ola Nestaas, General
Manager and Kjell Traa, Marketing Manager, PipeCare AS
* Use of High Strength for Deep and Ultra-Deepwater Large
Diameter Pipelines, Dr T Sriskandarajah and G Anurudran,
Kellogg Brown and Root Ltd

